{"ja309:0.1":"Jataka ","ja309:0.2":"Catukkanipata ","ja309:0.3":"Kalingavagga ","ja309:0.4":"9. Chavakajataka ","ja309:1.1":"“Sabbamidam carimam katam, ","ja309:1.2":"Ubho dhammam na passare; ","ja309:1.3":"Ubho pakatiya cuta, ","ja309:1.4":"Yo cayam mantejjhapeti; ","ja309:1.5":"Yo ca mantam adhiyati”. ","ja309:2.1":"“Salinam odanam bhunje, ","ja309:2.2":"sucim mamsupasecanam; ","ja309:2.3":"Tasma etam na sevami, ","ja309:2.4":"dhammam isihi sevitam”. ","ja309:3.1":"“Paribbaja maha loko, ","ja309:3.2":"pacantannepi panino; ","ja309:3.3":"Ma tam adhammo acarito, ","ja309:3.4":"asma kumbhamivabhida. ","ja309:4.1":"Dhiratthu tam yasalabham, ","ja309:4.2":"dhanalabhanca brahmana; ","ja309:4.3":"Ya vutti vinipatena, ","ja309:4.4":"adhammacaranena va”ti. ","ja309:5.1":"Chavakajatakam navamam. "}